  (165,2,1,1,'<p>ICANN as an organization has grown in the past few years, the number of participants, including those from the LAC region has increased. However, this has not necessarily resulted in a growing pool of active volunteers from the region nor have we experienced a greater number of contributions from our regional stakeholders in the various ICANN Policy Development Processes (PDPs).</p>\r\n<p>It’s important to support our regional stakeholders by providing the necessary tools in order for them to become active and meaningful participants in ICANN structure and PDPs.&nbsp;\r\n 				\r\n 			\r\n 		\r\n</p>\r\n<p></p>','','','','','','','','1','Policy Focus and meaningful participation','h1','','','','','','','','','','icann_2-en.png','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',22,4,'2019-04-03 11:46:19','2019-04-09 02:36:03','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (166,2,1,1,'<p>It’s with in ICANN mission to ensure that the Internet\'s unique identifier system remains secure and interoperable.</p>\r\n<p>We need to ensure that regional stakeholders are aware and have the technical skills to preserve and enhance the operational stability, reliability, security, and global interoperability of the Internet. At the same time we need to contribute to have a more robust and resilient DNS in the LAC Region.&nbsp;\r\n 				\r\n 			\r\n 		\r\n</p>\r\n<p></p>','','','','','','','','1','Healthy, stable and resilient unique identifier ecosystem','h1','','','','','','','','','','icann_3-en.png','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',23,4,'2019-04-03 11:46:19','2019-04-09 10:45:14','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (167,2,1,1,'<p>The DNS Industry in the LAC region is low in numbers compared to other regions, particularly in some sub regions such as the Caribbean and Central America. Competition, innovation and choice can help develop the domain name marketplace and can potentially incentivize active participation of new stakeholders from the region.</p>\r\n<p>This strategy should consider that there are countries in the Caribbean and in Central America that will require a different approach in the implementation of the projects under this Key Area of Interest.&nbsp;\r\n 				\r\n 			\r\n 		\r\n</p>\r\n<p><br></p>','','','','','','','','1','DNS Innovation, competition and choice','h1','','','','','','','','','','icann_4-en.png','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',24,4,'2019-04-03 11:46:19','2019-04-09 10:47:54','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
