  (193,2,1,1,'','Bruna Martins','Non-Commercial Users Constituency','Brazil','<p class=\"text-justify\"><strong>Bruna Martins dos Santos</strong> is an Internet Governance researcher at LAPIN/UnB, regional representative for Latin America and the Caribbean on the Executive Committee of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/Non-Commercial_Users_Constituency\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Non-Commercial Users Constituency\">Non-Commercial Users Constituency</a>&nbsp;and current co-coordinator the Internet Governance Caucus. She is based in Brasilia, Brazil.</p>','https://twitter.com/Boomartins','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','brunamartins.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:48:36','2019-05-07 15:48:36','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (194,2,1,2,'','Bartlett Morgan','ALAC member','Jamaica','<p><strong>Bartlett Morgan</strong>&nbsp;is a trained attorney-at-law. With roots in Jamaica, he currently resides in Barbados where, in 2012, he&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.lexcaribbean.com/attorneys/bartlett-morgan.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\">joined the team</a>&nbsp;at Lex Caribbean, Attorneys-at-Law, a pan-Caribbean corporate-commercial law firm.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Bartlett first became involved with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN\" title=\"ICANN\">ICANN</a>&nbsp;in 2013 when he joined the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://gnso.icann.org/en/group-activities/active/irtp-d\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\">IRTP-D working group</a>&nbsp;in the GNSO. Since then, he has become involved with At-Large where he is currently the ALS representative of the Barbados ICT Professionals Association (BIPA) to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/LACRALO\" title=\"LACRALO\">LACRALO</a>. In 2016, Bartlett was named as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN_Fellow\" title=\"ICANN Fellow\">Fellow</a>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN_57\" title=\"ICANN 57\">ICANN 57</a>&nbsp;in Hyderabad, India.</p>\r\n<p><br></p>','https://twitter.com/BartlettMorgan','https://www.linkedin.com/in/bartlettmorgan/','https://bartlettmorgan.com','','','','','','','','','','','','','bartlettmorgan_art.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:48:36','2019-05-07 15:48:36','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (195,2,1,3,'','Lance Hinds','GAC','Guyana','<p class=\"text-justify\"><strong>Lance Hinds</strong>&nbsp;is the CEO of Brain Street Group&nbsp;(Technologies). He is also a LACRALO member at ICANN. Hinds is a members of the Governmental Advisory Committee (GAC) representing the Government of Guyana.</p><p class=\"text-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"text-justify\"></p>','','https://www.linkedin.com/in/lance-hinds-7405971/','','','','','','','','','','','','','','lancehindscaricature.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:48:36','2019-05-07 15:48:36','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (196,2,1,4,'','Ernesto Bojorquez ‏  ','Commercial Director at NIC Mexico','Mexico','<p><strong>Ernesto Bojorquez</strong>&nbsp;is the Commercial Director at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/NIC_Mexico\" title=\"NIC Mexico\">NIC Mexico</a>; he has been working for the organization since 2002.</p>\r\n<p>Bojorquez has studied AT CETYS University and Northwestern University - Kellogg School of Management.</p>\r\n<p>Now he is President of LACTLD.&nbsp;</p>','https://twitter.com/ebojorquez','https://www.linkedin.com/in/ebojorquez/','','','','','','','','','','','','','','ernesto_b.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:48:36','2019-05-07 15:48:36','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (197,2,1,5,'','Miguel Ignacio Estrada','General Manager LACTLD','Argentina','<p><b>Miguel Ignacio Estrada</b>&nbsp;is the General Manager of LACTLD (Association of Administrators of TLD from Latin America and the Caribbean) since 2017. During 2017 he acted as an Advisor for the Undersecretary of TIC Regulation of Argentina. From 2016 until 2017 he was the National Director of Internet Policy and Development. He also served as the Communications Manager at the Argentinian&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/CcTLD\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"CcTLD\">ccTLD</a>&nbsp;operator,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/NIC_Argentina\" title=\"NIC Argentina\">NIC Argentina</a>, from 2012 until 2016.</p>','https://www.linkedin.com/in/acmuzic/','https://www.linkedin.com/in/acmuzic/?originalSubdomain=bo','','','','','','','','','','','','','','miguel-ignacio-estrada_caricature-2013.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:48:36','2019-05-07 15:48:36','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (198,2,1,6,'','Kevon Swift','Head of Strategic Relations and Integration LACNIC','Trinidad & Tobago','<p><b>Kevon Swift</b>&nbsp;is the Head of Strategic Relations and Integration at the Latin American and Caribbean Internet Addresses Registry (LACNIC). He is a proud Trinbagonian.</p>','https://twitter.com/swiffay?lang=es','https://www.linkedin.com/in/kevonswift/','','','','','','','','','','','','','','kevonswift_art.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:48:36','2019-05-07 15:48:36','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (199,2,1,7,'','Oscar Robles','CEO LACNIC','Mexico','<p><b>Oscar A. Robles-Garay</b>&nbsp;is currently CEO of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/LACNIC\" title=\"LACNIC\">LACNIC</a>. He has professional experiences in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/Domain_Name\" title=\"Domain Name\">domain names</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/IP_Address\" title=\"IP Address\">IP Address</a>&nbsp;space, Strategic Planning and Internet Governance.</p><p>Oscar has been working in Internet Governance since 1996. In 1997, he was included in the experts group conducted by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/WIPO\" title=\"WIPO\">WIPO</a>&nbsp;to comment on a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/RFC\" title=\"RFC\">RFC</a>&nbsp;series. He is a co-founder of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/LACTLD\" title=\"LACTLD\">LACTLD</a>&nbsp;and has been President of its Board of Directors two times. In 2005, he was appointed as an Advisory Council member for the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/PIR\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"PIR\">Public Interest Registry</a>, manager of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/GTLD\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"GTLD\">gTLD</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/.org\" title=\".org\">.org</a>. Apart from being active in the field he has teaching experience as well; he has taught e-commerce Legal Frameworks courses at the Virtual University of the Monterrey Institute of Technology in Mexico<br></p>','https://twitter.com/oscarrobles','https://www.linkedin.com/in/oscarrobles/','','','','','','','','','','','','','','oscar-robles-garay_caricature.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:48:36','2019-05-07 15:48:36','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (200,2,1,8,'','Leon Sanchez','ICANN Board of Directors','Mexico','<p><strong>Leon Sanchez</strong>&nbsp;is currently serving on the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN_Board\" title=\"ICANN Board\">ICANN Board of Directors</a>. He is a lawyer and head of the Intellectual Property Division for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/index.php?title=Fulton_%26_Fulton&action=edit&redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Fulton & Fulton (page does not exist)\">Fulton & Fulton</a>, a law firm in Mexico.</p>\r\n<p>He was an ICANN Fellow&nbsp;for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN_48\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ICANN 48\">ICANN 48</a>&nbsp;in Buenos Aires,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN_46\" title=\"ICANN 46\">ICANN 46</a>&nbsp;in Beijing, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN_44\" title=\"ICANN 44\">ICANN 44</a>&nbsp;in Prague. He is an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ALAC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ALAC\">ALAC</a>&nbsp;member appointed by the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/NomCom\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"NomCom\">NomCom</a>, as well as an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/IPC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"IPC\">IPC</a>&nbsp;member. Sanchez is involved in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ISOC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ISOC\">ISOC</a>&nbsp;Mexico\r\n</p>','https://twitter.com/lion05','https://www.linkedin.com/in/leonfelipe/','','','','','','','','','','','','','','leonsanchez-caricature.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:48:36','2019-05-07 15:48:36','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
  (209,2,1,9,'','Rafael Lito Ibarra','ICANN Board of Directors','El Salvador','<p><strong>Rafael Lito Ibarra</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;is currently serving on the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN_Board\" title=\"ICANN Board\">ICANN Board of Directors</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Lito was Director of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/index.php?title=RAICES&action=edit&redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"RAICES (page does not exist)\">RAICES</a>&nbsp;president of SVNET, the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/CcTLD\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"CcTLD\">ccTLD</a>&nbsp;operator for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/index.php?title=.sv&action=edit&redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\".sv (page does not exist)\">.sv</a>. He has been running .sv since 1993. He is a member of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/CcNSO\" title=\"CcNSO\">ccNSO</a>&nbsp;and on the boards of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/LACTLD\" title=\"LACTLD\">LACTLD</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/LACNIC\" title=\"LACNIC\">LACNIC</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/index.php?title=RedCLARA&action=edit&redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"RedCLARA (page does not exist)\">RedCLARA</a>.</p>','https://twitter.com/litoibarra','https://www.linkedin.com/in/lito-ibarra-969ba85/?originalSubdomain=sv','','','','','','','','','','','','','','rafael_b.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:53:06','2019-05-07 15:54:51','lac-admin','lac-admin',0),
