  (260,2,1,4,'<p>The LAC+i Roadshow is designed to raise awareness across the LAC region on key topics related to the DNS critical infrastructure such as the transition to IPv6, SSR (Security, Stability and Resiliency) and the impact of the new gTLD program, what is ICANN, how to participate and topics on the LAC DNS Industry</p>\r\n<p>To ensure a well distributed set of events there will be four editions of the LAC+i Roadshow per year: The Caribbean; Andean Region, Mexico and Central America and South America.\r\n</p>','','','','','','','','1','','h1','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',9,4,'2019-05-08 16:14:48','2019-05-08 16:17:12','lac-admin','lac-admin',0),
