  (262,2,1,7,'<p>The 2018 South American edition of the LAC-i Roadshow took place on August 16 2018&nbsp;in Montevideo, Uruguay.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.agesic.gub.uy/\" target=\"_blank\">AGECIC</a>, <a href=\"https://www.miem.gub.uy/\" target=\"_blank\">MIEM</a> and <a href=\"https://www.nic.uy/Registrar/\" target=\"_blank\">Uynic</a> were the local hosts, we had&nbsp;&nbsp;around 40 participants in this edition, who were very involved in the discussions.</p>','','','','','','','','2','','h1','','','','','','','','','','','roadshow_montevideo.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',9,4,'2019-05-08 16:22:41','2019-05-08 16:44:07','lac-admin','lac-admin',0),
