  (224,194,'slice_delete','2019-05-07 15:57:05','soporte-lac',2,1,2,'','Bartlett Morgan','ALAC member','Jamaica','<p><strong>Bartlett Morgan</strong>&nbsp;is a trained attorney-at-law. With roots in Jamaica, he currently resides in Barbados where, in 2012, he&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.lexcaribbean.com/attorneys/bartlett-morgan.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\">joined the team</a>&nbsp;at Lex Caribbean, Attorneys-at-Law, a pan-Caribbean corporate-commercial law firm.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Bartlett first became involved with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN\" title=\"ICANN\">ICANN</a>&nbsp;in 2013 when he joined the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://gnso.icann.org/en/group-activities/active/irtp-d\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\">IRTP-D working group</a>&nbsp;in the GNSO. Since then, he has become involved with At-Large where he is currently the ALS representative of the Barbados ICT Professionals Association (BIPA) to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/LACRALO\" title=\"LACRALO\">LACRALO</a>. In 2016, Bartlett was named as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN_Fellow\" title=\"ICANN Fellow\">Fellow</a>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://icannwiki.org/ICANN_57\" title=\"ICANN 57\">ICANN 57</a>&nbsp;in Hyderabad, India.</p>\r\n<p><br></p>','https://twitter.com/BartlettMorgan','https://www.linkedin.com/in/bartlettmorgan/','https://bartlettmorgan.com','','','','','','','','','','','','','bartlettmorgan_art.jpg','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',39,9,'2019-05-07 15:48:36','2019-05-07 15:48:36','soporte-lac','soporte-lac',0),
